      <title>SM Prime 将扩建菲律宾购物中心，稳定中国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/sm-prime-to-expand-philippine-malls-steady-china-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位高层官员透露，菲律宾最大的购物中心运营商 SM Prime Holdings Inc. 正在加速国内扩张计划，而不会大力投资竞争更为激烈的中国业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/sm-prime-to-expand-philippine-malls-steady-china-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:27:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
