      <title>中国人民银行开始交易国债以影响收益率曲线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/china-s-pboc-sells-long-term-bonds-buys-short-end-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行开始交易国债，这一举措备受期待，因为强劲的涨势使基准收益率跌至历史最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/china-s-pboc-sells-long-term-bonds-buys-short-end-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管估值过高，但 Robeco 仍看到价值空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-30/robeco-sees-pockets-of-value-despite-lofty-valuations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Robeco Institutional Asset Management 投资组合经理 Aliki Rouffiac 讨论了在经济放缓、“估值过高”和波动性上升的背景下股市的前景。“还有其他风险，比如美国选举风险，可能会造成更大的波动，但目前这可能被视为买入机会，”Rouffiac 告诉彭博电视台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-30/robeco-sees-pockets-of-value-despite-lofty-valuations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 09:13:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
